title: Mitch Cahalane
text:
Mitch Cahalane (born 5 May 1989) is an <a href="Australian%20people">Australian</a> professional <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> footballer who most recently played as a <a href="Rugby%20league%20positions%23Prop">prop</a> for <a href="Halifax%20R.L.F.C.">Halifax</a> in the <a href="Championship%20%28rugby%20league%29">Kingstone Press Championship</a>. 
Cahalane has played for the <a href="Mount%20Pritchard%20Mounties">Mount Pritchard Mounties</a> in the <a href="Intrust%20Super%20Premiership%20NSW">NSW Cup</a> and was previously in the system of the <a href="Penrith%20Panthers">Penrith Panthers</a>.
